comments.content: The molecular pathways of genes located at the region 11p11.2. A deletion in 11p11.2 can cause the Potocki-Shaffer syndrome (MIM # 601224) which is characterised by malformations in the heart, kidney and urinary tract. The chromosomal location was taken from Kirov et al. 2014 and literature cited there (chr11:43940000-46020000, GRCh37).
